'''Corey''' is a man who slept with [[Holly Harner]].

==History==
Corey had a one-night stand with Holly. The next day, he learned that she'd fallen down his stairs and was taken to the hospital. He showed up at the hospital and waited for her. Despite Holly telling them to tell him that she was dead, they didn't, so he continued to wait at the hospital. At the end of the day, Meredith told him he had no future with Holly, so he should go out and live his life.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
He had a one-night stand with [[Holly Harner]]. Despite only being one night, Corey believed they had really connected.

==Notes and Trivia==
*He slept through Holly falling down the stairs.
*Holly said he's the kind of guy who tells you he's going to tell you something before he just tells you.
